elp Themselves: Automatic Decomposition of Code Review Changes (Barnett et al. 2015)</a> (<a href=\"https://blog.acolyer.org/2015/06/26/helping-developers-help-themselves-automatic-decomposition-of-code-review-changes/\">summary on the morning paper</a>) Research into automatically splitting big diffs into smaller diffs leading to better reviews.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Articles</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/bguthrie/status/937750796334174209\">Brian Guthrie's Feature Branching Rant</a> Twitter thread on the pros and cons of GitHub's open source first model with regards to \"in-company\" code review practice.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Articles</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://blog.codinghorror.com/code-reviews-just-do-it/\">Code Reviews: Just Do It</a> Seminal post advocating for peer review of software back in 2006.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Articles</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/unpacking-trunk-club/designing-awesome-code-reviews-5a0d9cd867e3\">Designing Awesome Code Reviews</a> Principles for actively designing a code review process.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Articles</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.developer.com/tech/article.php/3579756/Effective-Code-Reviews-Without-the-Pain.htm\">Effective Code Reviews Without the Pain</a> Another 2006 classic on how to effectively perform a code review.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Articles</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://engineering.tumblr.com/post/170040992289/how-i-review-code\">How I review code</a> More personal advice on how to best review a pull request from an engineer at Tumblr.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Articles</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://kickstarter.engineering/pull-requests-how-to-get-and-give-good-feedback-f573469f0c44\">Pull Requests: How to Get and Give Good Feedback</a> Advice for both sides of the code review process, the reviewer and the reviewee.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Articles</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://blog.skyliner.io/ship-small-diffs-741308bec0d1\">Ship Small Diffs</a> Why it's better to review small changes rather than large ones.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Articles</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://blog.usejournal.com/the-art-of-humanizing-pull-requests-prs-b520588eb345\">The Art of Humanizing Pull Requests</a> Emoji rich guide to the human side of code review via pull requests.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Articles</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/@sandya.sankarram/unlearning-toxic-behaviors-in-a-code-review-culture-b7c295452a3c\">Unlearning Toxic Behaviors in a Code Review Culture</a> A how-to guide for pull requests via how-not-too.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Articles</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://medium.freecodecamp.org/why-i-changed-the-way-i-think-about-code-quality-88c5d8d57e68\">Why I changed the way I think about Code Quality</a> Why code quality is about more than just the code.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Books</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Handbook-Walkthroughs-Inspections-Technical-Reviews/dp/0932633196\">Handbook of Walkthroughs, Inspections, and Technical Reviews</a> Older book covering more formal walkthroughs but covers politics and group dynamics in review well.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Books</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Peer-Reviews-Software-Practical-Guide/dp/0201734850\">Peer Reviews in Software: A Practical Guide</a> A practical guide to formal code inspections as a code review practice.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Books</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Software-Inspection-Industry-Best-Practice/dp/0818673400\">Software Inspection: An Industry Best Practice</a> Compendium of papers on code review practice.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Books</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://leanpub.com/whattolookforinacodereview\">What to Look for in a Code Review</a> JetBrains sponsored ebook of how to spot coding anti-patterns during review.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Talks and Podcasts</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://confreaks.tv/videos/rubyconf2017-code-reviews-honesty-kindness-inspiration-pick-three\">Code Reviews: Honesty, Kindness, Inspiration: Pick Three - Jacob Stoebel RubyConf 2017</a> How to do effective code review while remaining kind to the original author.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"joho/awesome-code-review","categoryHTML":"<h2>Talks and Podcasts</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PJjmw9TRB7s\">Implementing a Strong Code-Review Culture - Derek Prior Railsconf 2015</a> How to instill a healthy code review culture in a team.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-07-23T04:26:57.000Z"}]}